// |----------------------------------------------------------------       ------------------------------------------------------------|
// |   CTRL   |    Z    |    X    |     C    |    V     |    B     |       |       |           |         |         |        |          |
     &kp LCTRL   &kp Z     &kp X     &kp C      &kp V      &kp B            &none     &none       &none     &none     &none     &none
// |----------------------------------------------------------------       ------------------------------------------------------------|
//                                |  ALT OPT |  GUI CMD |    L2    |       |       |           |         |
                                    &kp LALT   &kp LGUI    &mo 4            &none     &none       &none   
//                                |---------------------------------       ------------------------------|
                }
                crazy_test_layer_2 {
// |----------------------------------------------------------------       ------------------------------------------------------------|
// |  BCKSPC  |    Y    |    U    |    I     |    O     |    P     |       |       |           |         |         |        |          |
     &kp BSPC    &kp Y     &kp U     &kp I      &kp O       &kp P           &none     &none       &none     &none     &none     &none
// |----------------------------------------------------------------       ------------------------------------------------------------|
// |   SHFT   |    H    |    J    |     K    |     L    |   '  "   |       |       |           |         |         |        |          |
     &kp LSHFT   &kp H     &kp J     &kp K      &kp L     &kp SQT           &none     &none       &none     &none     &none     &none
// |----------------------------------------------------------------       ------------------------------------------------------------|
// |   CTRL   |    N    |    M    |     ,    |    .     |   /  ?   |       |       |           |         |         |        |          |
     &kp LCTRL   &kp N     &kp M    &kp COMMA   &kp DOT   &kp FSLH           &none     &none       &none     &none     &none     &none
